description:
Is Christ returning sooner than we think?

This #short video from Pastor Ted Wilson's weekly message reminds us that, not only did Jesus Christ create us, redeem us on the cross, and justify and purify us by His power, but He is also coming very soon to take us home. Let us be watchful and ready for His imminent coming. Study the Bible, especially the prophecies, as you've never done before, and share the everlasting Gospel.

Watch the entire video to hear Pastor Ted Wilson's message, which serves as a reminder to study the Scriptures faithfully and prepare for the return of our Lord, Jesus Christ.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8LKFR87VRkY&list=PL-k2Gb-DBYo_ANrUJhHN2_4bSlMDTjuqQ&index=46
